title: DAC7578 3D Render
summary: A rendered 3D view of the DAC7578 breakout board showing placement of IC, passives, connectors, and labeled breakout pads. The image uses a dark blue background and perspective camera angle.

structured_data.description: 3D CAD-style rendering with visible labels VRF, channels 0-7, GND, VCC, SCL, SDA, LDAC, and CLR. Two STEMMA QT connectors are shown at left and right, along with mounting holes and central DAC package.
